{"post":{"id":"1a5c2669-179b-445f-bdbe-9191a87af218","title":"Lalason, une assurance avant tout","excerpt":"Pourquoi s’abonner à Lalason, c’est s’assurer une tranquillité d’esprit totale À l’époque où La Musique Libre  n’était qu’un projet...","firstPublishedDate":"2025-05-13T15:33:22.723Z","lastPublishedDate":"2025-05-13T15:33:22.723Z","slug":"lalason-une-assurance-avant-tout","featured":false,"pinned":false,"categoryIds":[],"memberId":"b3f3fbbd-9b4e-46c0-b0e4-7edc60705954","hashtags":[],"commentingEnabled":true,"minutesToRead":2,"tagIds":[],"relatedPostIds":[],"pricingPlanIds":[],"language":"fr","richContent":{"nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"foo","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"gya52510","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Pourquoi s’abonner à Lalason, c’est s’assurer une tranquillité d’esprit totale","decorations":[{"type":"FONT_SIZE","fontSizeData":{"unit":"PX","value":20}}]}}],"headingData":{"level":1,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"zbhh3512","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"g65ko48212","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"997tg","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"À l’époque où ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"La Musique Libre","decorations":[{"type":"ITALIC","italicData":true}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" n’était qu’un projet passion sur YouTube, nous étions portés par une idée simple : partager de la bonne musique, libre de droit, avec la communauté des créateurs. Beaucoup d’artistes indépendants nous écrivaient pour nous dire : « Tu peux utiliser ma musique, elle est libre. » Alors on publiait. On faisait confiance. Et vous aussi.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"f0qiq634","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"5yo9x480","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Mais au fil du temps, une réalité plus complexe s’est imposée :","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"ce qui est libre aujourd’hui ne le reste pas forcément demain.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"u9nmr670","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"qwkv8355","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"VIDEO","id":"qettf354","nodes":[],"videoData":{"video":{"src":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_Ji3mi-kE0"},"duration":131.0},"thumbnail":{"src":{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/G_Ji3mi-kE0/maxresdefault.jpg"},"width":1280,"height":720},"title":"|Musique libre de droits| VDGL - Free"}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6dlon356","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"84d6c","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"1sw98590","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Quand le libre devient flou…","decorations":[]}}],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"k86fj705","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"r1wcv592","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"On a tous connu ce moment désagréable : une vidéo en ligne depuis des mois reçoit subitement une ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"réclamation pour atteinte aux droits d’auteur","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":". Pourquoi ? Parce que l’artiste qui avait rendu sa musique disponible sans restriction signe un contrat avec un label, ou décide de monétiser ses œuvres via une plateforme de gestion des droits. Résultat : la licence change… et votre vidéo devient un champ de mines.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"kgpye596","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"C’est arrivé à nous. C’est arrivé à vous. Et c’est exactement pour éviter cela que ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Lalason est né","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":".","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"iaz89747","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"sjbw7602","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Lalason, c’est plus qu’un catalogue. C’est une assurance.","decorations":[]}}],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"dr5nz859","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"8q8i3604","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Nous avons bâti Lalason comme une ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"solution professionnelle et durable","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":". Chaque titre que vous trouvez dans notre catalogue est soumis à un ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"contrat clair et formel","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" entre nous et l’artiste. Ce contrat nous donne l’assurance — et donc à vous aussi — que vous pouvez utiliser la musique ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"librement, sans mauvaise surprise","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" dans un an, deux ans, dix ans.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"nz86x898","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"a5imv612","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Quand vous vous abonnez à Lalason, vous accédez à :","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"sc4kp964","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6k2h5614","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"✅ Une musique de qualité, sélectionnée avec soin","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"v3n80932","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"✅ Des licences solides et permanentes","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6d0c5999","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"✅ Une protection contre les réclamations injustifiées","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"emrbo1034","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"✅ Un support réactif en cas de souci avec une plateforme comme YouTube, Facebook ou Instagram","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"8xn4y1070","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"0vn7t616","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Lalason, c’est la sérénité pour les créateurs","decorations":[]}}],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"qx1211106","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"zdr1i1176","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"r41l5618","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Créer du contenu, c’est déjà assez de boulot comme ça. Vous n’avez pas à perdre du temps à vérifier si tel morceau est encore « libre », si l’artiste a signé avec un label, ou si une réclamation automatique va tomber dans 6 mois.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ex7bj1247","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"9qj9a620","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Avec Lalason, vous pouvez vous concentrer sur ce qui compte : ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"créer.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"tsevi623","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Et nous, on s’occupe du reste.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"hfmwa1215","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"vpzbu1145","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"p1tv0625","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"\uD83C\uDFA7 ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Abonnez-vous à Lalason, et libérez-vous vraiment des soucis liés aux droits d’auteur.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"5m9nj628","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Parce qu’au fond, la vraie musique libre, c’est celle qui ne revient pas vous hanter.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"scp6d2075","nodes":[],"headingData":{"level":3,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}}],"documentStyle":{}},"preview":false,"contentId":"682366429958032abf8bb551","mostRecentContributorId":"b3f3fbbd-9b4e-46c0-b0e4-7edc60705954","media":{"wixMedia":{"image":{"id":"b3f3fb_7a14358f6c9a41b1931da23d37913ad7~mv2.webp","url":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/b3f3fb_7a14358f6c9a41b1931da23d37913ad7~mv2.webp","height":1024,"width":1792,"filename":"DALL·E 2025-05-13 17.32.48 - A modern and clean visual representing the concept of music licensing protection. In the center, a relaxed, gender-neutral content creator wearing hea.webp"}},"displayed":true,"custom":true},"hasUnpublishedChanges":false,"translations":[],"customExcerpt":false,"internalCategoryIds":[],"internalRelatedPostIds":[]}}